    "name": "Starbug Troopers : The 4 horseflies of the apocalypse",
    "steam_appid": 3160110,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As Bea prepares to become the 7th <strong>Starbug Trooper</strong>, the ceremony is interrupted by an attack. <strong>The 4 Horseflies of the Apocalypse</strong>  return after years of absence. Bea must unite all the Starbug Troopers to put an end to the schemes of <strong>Lies, Famine, Plague, and Conquest</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160110/extras/587ce497dbf58531f249e6913b78a930.avif?t=1767628911\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160110/extras_big/587ce497dbf58531f249e6913b78a930.avif?t=1767628911 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AN ORIGINAL BLEND OF GENRES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the adventures of Bea and the other Starbug Troopers in a humorous journey that mixes strategy and action. <strong>Outsmart your opponent</strong> by positioning your troops to your advantage and gain the upper hand. Or perhaps you'd prefer to <strong>outpace them</strong>, using your reflexes and agility to destroy all their ships.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A STRATEGY BASED ON SUPPORT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increase your chances of victory in combat : position your troops relative to each other to <strong>gain greater support than your opponent</strong> and stack the odds in your favor during battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160110/extras/2a831ff41e2a288f07f535f5eb59992f.poster.avif?t=1767628911\" width=800 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160110/extras/2a831ff41e2a288f07f535f5eb59992f.webm?t=1767628911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160110/extras/2a831ff41e2a288f07f535f5eb59992f.mp4?t=1767628911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MINI SHIPS, MAXI COMBAT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore environments at the scale of an insect. Carve your way through tall grass, navigate upstream rivers, or delve into a mysterious cavern in search of your opponents, <strong>destroying their ships before they find you</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160110/extras/b1b4fc41b8429cf621c4065bdb353db0.poster.avif?t=1767628911\" width=800 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160110/extras/b1b4fc41b8429cf621c4065bdb353db0.webm?t=1767628911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160110/extras/b1b4fc41b8429cf621c4065bdb353db0.mp4?t=1767628911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RECRUIT YOUR TROOPS FROM 7 UNIQUE SHIP TYPES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Seven unique insect-ships are available</strong>. Fighter, healer, bomber... Each ship has its own role and unique abilities. It’s up to you to recruit the right ships to lead you to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160110/extras/0b01e19cd91e521d46a8531c4a0defa2.poster.avif?t=1767628911\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160110/extras/0b01e19cd91e521d46a8531c4a0defa2.webm?t=1767628911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160110/extras/0b01e19cd91e521d46a8531c4a0defa2.mp4?t=1767628911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SKIRMISH</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come discover the brand-new Skirmish mode<br>· Random map generation, in the size of your choice<br>· Select up to 6 enemies<br>· Battle in one of the game’s four original environments</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >… then start again on a new map, for endless replayability!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An epic journey into the heart of the first green space opera.</p>",
